headline: ‘Fastest-Growing Market in Software’: Morgan Stanley Suggests 2 Cybersecurity Stocks to Buy
summary: ‘Tech’ gets more than its share of headlines and hype, and rightfully so. Technology stocks have been major drivers of the market’s gains over the past few years, and everyone is interested in following the leaders. But tech is a broad word; it includes a wide range of categories – which brings us to cybersecurity software.
